skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: suggest a date
des: Whether you are indecisive, drawing a blank, or just looking for something new to keep your dates fresh, this skill will provide a variety of date ideas upon request. No additional hardware or account requirements necessary. Now you just need to find someone to go on a date with!
